load ../owned-harness-loop.maude

--- Coverage (leaf-ness positive): a gate-open kind (started) derives its fact, so
--- the search and the leaf-ness bites below have teeth.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  obs(started)
  =>* C:Cfg fact(started) .

--- Coverage (brokering): with the kernel mediation capability, a requested tool
--- is brokered and a tool result is reachable.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  running brokerEnabled toolReqPending
  =>* C:Cfg obs(toolRes) .

--- Coverage (single terminal): a running turn reaches a terminal fact.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  running
  =>* C:Cfg termFact(completed) .

--- Bite (leaf-ness, model_request): an interior observation never derives a
--- rule-matchable fact. The RESIDUAL soup var means any fact in any reachable
--- state is a solution, so No solution proves the gate stays closed.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  obs(modelReq)
  =>* fact(modelReq) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite (leaf-ness, tool_requested): same, for tool calls.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  obs(toolReq)
  =>* fact(toolReq) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite (leaf-ness, tool_result): same, for tool results.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  obs(toolRes)
  =>* fact(toolRes) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite (brokering): with no kernel mediation capability, a requested tool can
--- never reach a tool result -- the model cannot touch the tool directly.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  running toolReqPending
  =>* obs(toolRes) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite (single terminal): a running turn cannot hold two terminal facts at once;
--- the terminal transition consumes `running`.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-LOOP :
  running
  =>* termFact(completed) termFact(failed) RESIDUAL:Cfg .
